<doc>
  <member name="EMRPIXELFORMAT">
    <summary>
      <para>The <b>EMRPIXELFORMAT</b> structure contains the members for the <see cref="SetPixelFormat" /> enhanced metafile record. The pixel format information in <see cref="ENHMETAHEADER" /> refers to this structure.</para>
    </summary>
    <seealso cref="ENHMETAHEADER" />
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/gdi/metafile-structures">Metafile Structures</seealso>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/gdi/metafiles">Metafiles Overview</seealso>
    <seealso cref="PIXELFORMATDESCRIPTOR" />
    <seealso cref="SetPixelFormat" />
  </member>
  <member name="EMRPIXELFORMAT.emr">
    <summary>
      <para>The base structure for all record types.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="EMRPIXELFORMAT.pfd">
    <summary>
      <para>A
<see cref="PIXELFORMATDESCRIPTOR" /> structure, which describes the pixel format.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>